title: Three fined for parties on same day as No 10 event
content: The people who held or went to unlawful gatherings on 18 December last year saw their cases end in fines.

title: Gove, Shapps and Raab self-isolate after meeting
content: The three ministers came into close contact with Australia's deputy PM, who was later diagnosed with Covid.

title: Boris and Carrie Johnson announce birth of a girl
content: Boris and Carrie Johnson announce the birth of healthy daughter, their second child since he became prime minister.

title: Stratton quits as adviser after party video row
content: The tearful ex-journalist apologised, saying she would "regret the remarks for the rest of my days".
